name: .JSD File Extension
summary: Learn about .JSD files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: File used by Jazer, a personal and professional financial management program for Windows; saved in a binary format and contains the user's financial data; replaced by the .JSDA format in later Jazer software versions.

content: Jazer is available in three different editions:
Jazer 100 - Personal finances for home use
Jazer 200 - Academic personal finance for classrooms
